text: Angela Michelle "Angie" Harmon (born August 10, 1972) is a fashion model and actress. She appeared on the covers of ELLE and Esquire magazines. Harmon also acted in television series including Rizzoli & Isles, Law & Order and Baywatch. == References == Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:American television actors Category:Models from Texas
